title: Zend Performance Suite 3.6.0 (Linux) - REQ: v4.0.0
description:
Zend Performance Suite (ZPS) is the complete performance management solution for delivering PHP-based dynamic content cost-effectively.

ZPS, based on Zend's state-of-the-art dynamic content caching, code acceleration and file compression technologies is a single solution that will dramatically improve the number of customers your server will be able to handle.
